Package com.kolyadko.likeit.command.impl.showcommand

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ShowCommand
    Abstract class for show commands (which are sent by GET request and recognized by URI)
    ShowCreateQuestionPageCommand
    Command prepares RequestContent object to show createQuestion.jsp with data
    ShowCreateSectionPageCommand
    Command prepares RequestContent object to show createSection.jsp with data
    ShowDefaultContentCommand
    Command prepares RequestContent object to show any jsp page (fills it with default data such as top5 questions)
    ShowEditCommentPageCommand
    Command prepares RequestContent object to show editComment.jsp with data
    ShowEditProfilePageCommand
    Command prepares RequestContent object to show editProfile.jsp with data

    Command prepares RequestContent object to show editQuestion.jsp with data

    ShowHomePageCommand
    Command prepares RequestContent object to show home.jsp with data
    ShowProfilePageCommand
    Command prepares RequestContent object to show profile.jsp with data
    ShowQuestionListCommand
    Command prepares RequestContent object to show question.jsp with data This jsp is used to show different data: top questions, recent questions and question from particular section
    ShowQuestionPageCommand
    Command prepares RequestContent object to show question.jsp with data
    ShowRecentQuestPageCommand
    Command prepares RequestContent object to show question.jsp with recent questions data
    ShowSectionQuestPageCommand
    Command prepares RequestContent object to show question.jsp with questions from particular section data
    ShowTopQuestPageCommand
    Command prepares RequestContent object to show question.jsp with top questions data
    ShowUserListPageCommand
    Command prepares RequestContent object to show userList.jsp with data
